hadiths[35]{hadithnumber,text}:
743,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to Taqriban sola (16) mahiney Baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh kar key namaz padhtey rahey, phir aap ka rukhe-anwar Kaabey ki taraf kar diya gaya. eik aadmi jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Kaabey ki taraf munh kar key) namaz padhi thi, Ansaar ki eik qom (banu Haarisa) key paas sey guzra. (woh Baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh kar key namaz padh rahey they) us ney kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Kaba rukh namaz padhney ka hukm dey diya gaya hai, chunanche wo (namaz hi mein) Kabey ki taraf mud gaey."
744,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) safar mein apni sawari par ( nafl ) namaz padh liya kartey they. sawari ka munh jis taraf bhi hota. Imam Malik ney kaha : (Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key shagrid ) Abdullah bin Dinar ney kaha ke ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bhi aisey hi kiya kartey they.
745,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sawari par ( nafl ) namaz padh liya kartey they jis taraf bhi us ka munh hota. aur aap sawari par witr padh liya kartey they, magar farz namaz sawari par nahin padhtey they."
746,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke eik dafa log qubaa (ki masjid) mein subah ki namaz padh rahey they ke eik aaney wala unkey paas aaya aur us ney kaha : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par aaj raat ""wahi"" utri hai aur aap ko Kaabey ki taraf munh karney ka hukm diya gaya hai, lihaza tum bhi Kaabey ki taraf munh kar lo. unkey chehrey Sham ki taraf they, wo Kaabey ki taraf ghoom gaey."
747,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ghazwae-tabuk mein namazi key sutrey key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : paalaan ki pichhli lakdi key barabar hona chahiye.
748,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney samney neza gaad letey, phir uski taraf namaz padhtey."
749,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abu-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs sutrey ki taraf namaz padhey to us sey qarib khada ho (taake) shetan uski namaz ko kaat na dey."
750,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam),Usaama bin Zaid, Bilal aur Usman bin Talha (Hajabi) Raziallahu anhum Kaabey mein dakhil huye aur darwaza band kar liya. jab aap bahar tashrif laye to mainey Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaabey mein kya kiya? unhoney kaha : aap ney eik sutoon apney baain kiya aur do sutoon apney daeyn kiye aur teen sutoon apney peechhey un dino Baitullah chhe sutonon par qaaim tha, phir aap ney namaz padhi aur apney aur qibley ki deewar key darmiyan taqriban teen haath ka fasla kiya."
751,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey eik aadmi khada namaz padh raha ho to agar uskey samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi key barabar koi chiz ho to wo suttarah ban jati hai aur agar uskey samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi key barabar koi chiz na ho to aurat, gadhaa aur kaalaa kutta uski namaz tod detey hain. mainey kaha : kaley,  zard aur surkh mein kya farq hai? to Abu-Zar ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha tha jaisey tum ney mujh sey puchha hai to aap ney farmaya tha : kaalaa kutta shetan hai."
752,Hazrat Qatada sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Zaid sey puchha : kon si chiz namaz ko tod deti hai? unhoney kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : haiz wali aurat aur kutta. Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha ke Hazrat Shoba ney is riwayat ko marfooa bayan kiya hai.
753,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke main aur Fazal bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma apni eik gadhi par aaye jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Arfa mein logon ko namaz padha rahey they. hum kuchh saf key aagey sey guzrey, phir utar padey aur gadhi ko charney key liye chhod diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein kuchh nahin kaha."
754,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamari basti mein Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey milney tashrif laye. hamarey yahaan eik chhoti si kutiyaa aur eik gadhi thi jo charti phirti thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki namaz padhi aur ye dono aap key aagey thin. na unhein roka gaya aur na peechhey hataayaa gaya.
755,Hazrat Suheb sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko farmatey suna ke wo aur banu Haashim ka eik ladka eik gadhey par sawar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney sey guzrey jab ke aap namaz padh rahey they. hum dono utrey aur aap key sath mil kar namaz padhi. aap ney namaz na chhodi aur banu Abdul-Muttalib sey do chhoti bachchiyaan bhaagti hui aayin aur unhoney aap key ghutnon ko pakad liya. aap ney un dono ko alag kiya lekin namaz nahin chhodi.
756,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney leti hoti thi jab ke aap namaz padh rahey hotey they. jab main uthney ka irada karti to pasand na karti ke sidhi khadi hun aur aap key aagey sey guzrun is liye main leti leti khisak jati.
757,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid ney Basar bin Saeed ko Hazrat Abu Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja ke un sey puchhey ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey namazi key aagey sey guzarney waley key barey mein kya suna hai? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : agar namazi key aagey sey guzarney wala jaan ley ke is par is kaam ka kis qadr gunah hai to uskey liye chaalis (saal ya mahiney ya din) tak rukey rehna uskey aagey sey guzarney sey behtar ho.
758,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi namaz padhta ho to wo kisi ko apney aagey sey na guzarney dey. agar wo inkar karey to us sey ladaai karey."
759,"Hazrat Kasir apney walid sey bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey phir Baitullah key samney khadey ho kar maqame Ibrahim key eik kinarey key sath do rakatein padhin aur aap key aur tawaf karney walon key darmiyan koi na tha."
760,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko namaz padhtey they aur main aap key aur qibley key darmiyan aap key bistar par arz key rukh leti hoti thi. jab aap witr padhney ka irada farmatey to mujhey jagaa detey aur main witr padh leti.
761,"Hazrat Abu-Marsad Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabron ki taraf namaz na padho aur na un par betho."
762,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke merey ghar main eik tasaaweer wala kapda tha. mainey usey ghar main eik taaq key samney (bator parda) latka liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us taaq ki taraf namaz padha kartey they, is liye aap ney kaha : aey Aaisha ! isey merey samney sey hata do. mainey utaar kar uskey takiye bana liye."
763,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chataai thi jisey aap din ko bichha letey they aur raat ko us sey hujra sa bana letey they aur is mein namaz padhtey logon ko aap ki namaz ka pata chal gaya to wo aap ki namaz key sath namaz padhney lagey jab ke unkey aur aap key darmiyan wo chataai haael (rukawat) thi. aap ney farmaya : itney amal key shauqeen bano jiski aasani key sath taqat rakho kyonkey Allah Taala (sawab deney sey) nahin uktaaeyga yahan tak ke tum hi uktaa jaaogey (aur wo nek kaam chhod dogey). Allah Taala ka sab sey pasandida kaam wo hai jis par hameshgi ho agar-che wo thoda hi ho. phir aap ney us jagah namaz padhni chhod di. dobara nahin padhi (phir ghar mein padhney lagey) yahan tak ke Allah Taala ney aap ki rooh qabz kar li. aur aap jab koi kaam shuru kartey to is par hameshgi kartey (ye nahin ke chaar din kiya, phir chhod diya)."
764,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik kapdey mein namaz padhney key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : kya tum mein sey har shakhs key paas do do kapdey hain?
765,"Hazrat umr bin abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key ghar main eik kapdey mein namaz padhtey huye dekha hai, is tarah ke aap ney uskey dono kinarey apney dono kandhon par daley huye they."
766,Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya ke kabhi mein shikar key peechhey hota hun aur mujh par sirf eik qamis hoti hai to kya is mein namaz padh liya karun? aap ney farmaya : usey batan laga liya karo agar-che kaantey hi sey ho.
767,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke kuch log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padha kartey they aur unhoney apney izaar ( chhotey honey ki wajeh sey) bachon ki tarah gardan par baandhey hotey they to ( ehtiyati taur par ) aurton sey kaha gaya ke tum sajdey sey sar na uthaya karo yahan tak ke mard sidhey beth jaya karen.
768,Hazrat Amr bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab meri qom key log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey lotey to unhoney kaha ke aap ney farmaya tha : tumhari imaamat wo shakhs kiraey jo Quran Majeed ziyada padha huwa ho. to unhoney mujhey bulaya ( kyonkey mujhey ziyada Quran yad tha ) aur mujhey rukoo aur sajdey ka tariqa sikhaya to main unhein namaz padhaya karta tha aur mujh par eik phati hui chadar thi. log merey walid sey kehtey they : kya tum hamari nazron sey apney betey ki sharmgah nahin dhanp saktey?
769,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko namaz padhtey aur main aap key eik taraf leti hoti jab ke main haaiza hoti thi. mujh par eik chadar hoti thi jis ka kuch hissa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par hota tha.
770,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs is tarah eik kapdey mein namaz na padhey ke uskey kandhon par kuch bhi kapda na ho.
771,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik resham ki achkan yani sherwani sey milta julta libas tohfey mein diya gaya. aap ney usey pehna phir is mein namaz padhi. salam pheraa to usey badi tezi aur sakhti sey utaar diya, goya ke aap usey napasand farma rahey hain, phir farmaya : ye perhezgaron key liye jayez nahin."
772,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik dhaari daar munaqqash chadar mein namaz padhi, phir farmaya : mujhey iskey naqsh aur nigaar ney apni taraf mutawajjeh rakha. isey Abu-Jahm key paas ley jaao aur us sey uski (anbijaani) chadar ley aao."
773,"Hazrat Abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) surkh hulley (jodey) mein tashrif laye, eik barchhaa gaada aur uski taraf namaz padhi. kuttey gadhey aur aurten uskey aagey sey guzartey they."
774,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, farmati hain ke main aur Abul-Qaasim Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik kapdey mein sotey they. kabhi main haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. agar us kapdey ko mujh sey koi haiz waghera lag jata to itni jagah dho letey, mazeed jagah nahin dhotey they aur is mein namaz bhi padhtey they, phir dobara merey sath let jatey. agar phir koi chiz lag jati to dobara isi tarah dhotey. us sey zayed jagah na dhotey they."
775,"Hazrat Hamaam ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney peshab kiya, phir pani mangwaya aur wuzu kiya aur apney mozon par masah kiya. phir uthey aur namaz padhi. un sey is barey mein puchha gaya to farmaney lagey : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
776,Hazrat Abu-Muslima Saeed bin Yazid Basri ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik Raziallahu anhu sey puchha : kya Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jooton mein namaz padh letey they? unhoney farmaya : haan.
777,Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din namaz padhi to aap ney apney jooton ko apni baain taraf rakha.
